On the border of Hungary there were clashes of migrants with the police.
The refugees staged protests on the border of Serbia near the Hungarian settlement of Reske, which turned into clashes with law enforcement officers.
As a result, the Hungarian police used water cannons and tear gas, reports Reuters.
